subtivals (1.2.0-1) stable; urgency=low

  * Progress bar on each subtitle
  * Bold and italic support
  * Subtitles highlighting in list view
  * Next subtitle is selected while waiting
  * Disable calibration while playing
  * Enhance SSA positioning
  * Rework screen vertical positioning
  * SubRip positioning configuration at file open
  * Multiple styles edition
  * Disable next for while after subtitles change
  * Code refactor on playing control
  * Fix next if simultaneous subtitles

 -- Mathieu Leplatre <contact@mathieu-leplatre.info>  Thu, 21 Jun 2012 22:45:31 +0100

subtivals (1.1.0-1) stable; urgency=low

  * SubRip (.srt) support
  * Highlight current and next subtitles in main window
  * Ability to change screen background color
  * Reduced width of main window
  * Drag-and-drop support
  * Keyboard shortcuts working everywhere
  * Stop shortcut
  * Stop behaviour changed
  * Toggle calibration
  * Timeout now uses characters based duration
  * Remove resize with double-clic
  * Allow scrolling while playing
  * + Bug fixes

 -- Mathieu Leplatre <contact@mathieu-leplatre.info>  Thu, 14 May 2012 09:45:31 +0100
 
